1970;;The People Next Door;;American;;David Greene;;Eli Wallach, Julie Harris, Deborah Winters;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_People_Next_Door_(1970_film);;A married couple, Arthur and Gerrie Mason struggle with the realities of their imperfect marriage as they fight to save and rehabilitate their teenage daughter, Maxie, from having been led into a life of drug addiction and ultimate committal to a mental ward.